getReferenceVBEPlot

Source: R/plotting-functions.R
getReferenceVBEPlot.Rd

Generates plots of the virtual bioequivalence for the reference drug.

getReferenceVBEPlot(
  refAndTestSimulationsInVirtualPopulation,
  referenceDrugName = "Reference",
  testDrugName = "Test",
  yDimension = NULL,
  yUnit = NULL,
  timeUnit = ospsuite::ospUnits$Time$min
)

Arguments

refAndTestSimulationsInVirtualPopulation

A data frame containing the simulated plasma concentrations for the reference and test drugs.

referenceDrugName

The name of the reference drug.

testDrugName

The name of the test drug.

yDimension

The dimension of the y-axis.

yUnit

The unit of the y-axis.

timeUnit

The unit of the time axis.
